            "class": "EarthLike",
            "hideonmap": false,
            "description": "Grapeseed is an earthlike world of fertile valleys, inland seas, and temperate farming regions, with orderly port-cities tied to orbital freight traffic. It is known for a practical, dependable culture built around agriculture, trade, and quiet commercial stability."
